headline: Motorola Solutions Named Official Safety Technology Supplier of the Ryder Cup through 2027
summary: CHICAGO, June 02, 2025--Motorola Solutions (NYSE: MSI) has today been named the Official Safety Technology Supplier of the 2025 and 2027 Ryder Cup, professional golf’s renowned biennial team competition between the United States and Europe.
